WHO   — Gaius Helen Mohiam — the Reverend Mother of the gom jabbar
WHAT  — The Bene Gesserit Reverend Mother and Truthsayer to the Emperor who tests the boy Paul with the gom jabbar.
WHERE — D1 · Dune  Framework inputs: The Bene Gesserit  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — She embodies the Sisterhood's cold, millennia-long patience and its willingness to spend any life for the plan.
HOW   — She holds the box of pain at his hand and the poisoned needle at his neck, judging whether he is human enough to live.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  The needle waits at the throat of every soul she would call human.

